sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant VLLM as vLLM Container<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant TGIS as vllm-tgis-adapter<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant GPU as AMD ROCm GPU<br/>HIP/ROCm
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over VLLM,S3: Flow 3: Model Weight Download (startup)
    VLLM->>HF: GET model weights<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (HF_TOKEN)
    HF-->>VLLM: Model artifacts
    Note over VLLM,S3: Alternative: S3 storage
    VLLM->>S3: GET model weights<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials
    S3-->>VLLM: Model artifacts

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 1: OpenAI-compatible HTTP Inference
    Client->>RBAC: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    RBAC->>VLLM: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTP/8000 (localhost)<br/>No Auth (trusted)
    VLLM->>GPU: Inference computation<br/>HIP/ROCm
    GPU-->>VLLM: Tensor results
    VLLM-->>RBAC: JSON response
    RBAC-->>Client: JSON response<br/>HTTPS

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 2: TGIS gRPC Inference
    Client->>TGIS: GenerationService RPC<br/>gRPC/8033<br/>No Auth (pod-level)
    TGIS->>VLLM: Internal inference call
    VLLM->>GPU: Inference computation<br/>HIP/ROCm
    GPU-->>VLLM: Tensor results
    VLLM-->>TGIS: Inference result
    TGIS-->>Client: gRPC response
